The Forty Weeks skill has answers to your pregnancy questions from real parents’ experiences. 

This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or dignosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
